<plot>Widescreen documentary about designing and building one of the world's most energy efficient, high performance buildings - the US Green Building Council LEED CS Platinum rated Banner Bank Building in Boise, Idaho. Built for standard costs using standard parts put together in an integrated way, this 11 story building shows that building green is good business and good for the environment.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?222675</url></doc>
